<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Question Reply Mail</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="width: 100vw; height: 50vh;">
        <div style="width: 45%; height: 13%; background-color: lightblue; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 20px;">
            <h1 style="font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(77, 109, 104,0.9);
            letter-spacing: 2px; ">E-Learning</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="height: 87%; width: 45%; background-color: rgb(223, 235, 235); padding: 20px; ">
            <h1 style="font-size: large; font-family: gilroy;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 5px;
            ">Question Reply</h1>
            <p style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: medium;">Hello <%= name %></p>
            <p style="font-size: medium">A reply has been added to your question in the video <b><%=title%>.</b></p>
            <p style="font-size: medium">Please login to add reply and continue discussion.</p>
            <p style="font-size: medium">Thank you for being part of our community.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>